summary:
I am passionate about solving complex internal and external problems. I enjoy helping others formally and informally. I am capable of having a well-argumented discussion with my peers regarding any topic I am knowledgeable in. Finally, I often get fascinated and interested by listening to the passions of others, and I gladly tell others about mine. 

Want to know more about me? Connect with me and send me a message!
